{"tid":2000653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時係街見到d男仔就好似見到自己影子","createTime":"2020-05-04T04:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T04:28:35.000Z","uid":58316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f65f84485405f34e2ecefe46eff4b8314a65ece","tid":2000653,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"着住對拖鞋係街度買飯食<br />\n買完飯即刻行返上樓<br />\n前路茫茫<br />\n過一日得一日<br />\n食埋今餐先算<br />\n落街耷低頭<br />\n唔想理任何野<br />\n任何人同事<br />\n因為做人已經做到好攰<br />\n除左自己d野已經冇閒心餘力理<br />\n衰d講句<br />\n好過道友少少<br />\n爭在未用白粉麻醉自己<br />\n但都差唔多<br />\n好似藍潔瑛咁<br />\n最鍾意訓覺<br />\n因為訓覺可以發夢<br />\n逃避現實<br />\n或者塞住對耳聽歌<br />\n諗返自己d野<br />\n又一個下晝"},{"pid":"262709621798298e3724cb4ae02534f6191f7907","tid":2000653,"uid":78135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"你見到我？"},{"pid":"299d00d5130d9470ec0ee5c76df683a69bef7aa4","tid":2000653,"uid":336269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"262709621798298e3724cb4ae02534f6191f7907","tid":2000653,"uid":78135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:23:59.000Z","msg":"你見到我？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"嘘じゃない"},{"pid":"90eaff70c3a1bdd11e589760e046064dc5b2bd6e","tid":2000653,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:24:57.000Z","msg":"有份工返咪算係咁囉"},{"pid":"e2cd3fc7630d6b0e336e6871fc98c4eceafff6ce","tid":2000653,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"我工都無"},{"pid":"05c4b5da1361096d65d5ca6ba1c571043f4dbafb","tid":2000653,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:28:35.000Z","msg":"耷低頭唔會見到其他人，因為唔想有眼神接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}